pageContext.claim: “I won at the Supreme Court, they didn't even report it, yeah. And they still say he lost on the travel ban, he lost, he lost, but they are talking about the first two courts. They forget to say that the Supreme Court ruled -- this is the most dishonest people. It's hard to believe actually, but look at all those cameras, that's a lot.”
pageContext.analysis: The Supreme Court’s decision to uphold Trump’s travel ban was widely covered by news organizations.
